Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:43.16,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}迷い込んでいる　迷路の　出口はどこか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:45.45,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}異常が日常になって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.45,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}反則だ　待て待て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.41,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}別に　どうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:52.12,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}素直になれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:56.00,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}いつまでも　このままでいたいかも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.01,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}そんな気持ちは溶けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:08.68,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}僕らは探してた　お揃いの心を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:16.81,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}僕らは交わしてた　まとまらないセリフを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:24.95,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}触れたい手の熱が　心まで届いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.95,0:22:33.04,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}僕は背伸びしてた　大人びてる君を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:36.67,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}知りたいんだ　君のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:38.71,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}近づきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.84,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}夢じゃ足りなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:42.80,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}心が痛くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:47.14,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}もっと　言葉にしたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:34.90,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(0,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}夕阳下的我们是那么近  是那么懵懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:43.16,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}失去了方向  找寻不到出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:45.45,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}不普通的日子成了日常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.45,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}这犯规了  你先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.41,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}其实都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:52.12,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我只是无法坦诚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:56.00,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}或许我想要永远这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.01,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}这份感情已溶于我心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:08.68,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我们一直在寻找  那颗成对的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:16.81,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我们一直在相互诉说  那不成文的一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:24.95,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}透过掌心的温暖  直击内心的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.95,0:22:33.04,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我一直在逞强  看着像个小大人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:36.67,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}好想要更了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:38.71,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}好想靠近一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.84,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}不想只是梦到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:42.80,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}心里满是纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:47.14,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}好想告诉你
